    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require companies to publish wait time on phones, with fines for excessive waits",
        "additional_details": "I believe that many businesses are abusing customers with ridiculous under-staffing in a necessary function. It is unfair that a consumer is treated thus when the business won\u2019t accept email communications. All too often I spend many hours being kept on hold in order to have a 1 minute conversation with a service provider. Why is the customer\u2019s time treated as if of such little value to save the business the cost of staffing appropriately? I believe that it is abusive in the modern era.",
        "background": "Require the quarterly publication of statistics for phone queuing and fine businesses who have excessive wait times.",
